These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, entrepreneur, mechanic, paramedic, photographer, social-worker, videographer
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, subway, bus, motorbike, train, van
 1. the paramedic is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is the paramedic##1
 3. the videographer is on the right of the social-worker##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 5. the mechanic is in the middle##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
 7. the photographer is the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the electrician is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 9. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person driving the bus is on the left of the mechanic##1
11. the videographer is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | photographer | paramedic | entrepreneur | mechanic | electrician | social-worker | videographer |
| Transport   | airplane    | motorbike   | bus      | train | subway    | quad-bike    | van         |

