.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: martial-arts, zombie, drama, spy, scientific, action, crime
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, funk, gospel, pop, punk, rock, soul
 1. the fan of punk is the person watching spy movies##1
 2. the person watching action movies is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 3. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
 4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 6. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 7. the fan of punk is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of punk is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the fan of soul is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
10. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre          | martial-arts | zombie | scientific | spy | action | crime | drama |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | gospel   | pop   | punk      | d&b       | soul       | rock     |

