.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: poppy, marigold, lily, aconite, sunflower, iris, begonia
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, egyptian, indian, indonesian, nigerian, thai
 1. the person who growssunflower is the australian##1
 2. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 3. the nigerian is on the right of the egyptian##1
 4. the argentine is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 5. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 6. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
 7. the egyptian is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 8. the person who growslily is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the person who growslily is the indonesian##1
10. the indonesian is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
11. the thai is the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Flower   | iris    | begonia     | aconite     | lily      | marigold | sunflower      | poppy     |
| Nationality   | indian | egyptian | nigerian | indonesian | thai | australian | argentine |

