.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  mechanic, police-officer, dancer, freelancer, lawyer, security-guard, social-worker
7 different pets are kept: dog, fish, frog, goldfish, guinea-pig, horse, snake
 1. the police-officer is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the lawyer##1
 3. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the security-guard##1
 6. the lawyer is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the social-worker##1
 8. the dancer is on the right of the police-officer##1
 9. the freelancer is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the lawyer is on the right of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Job   | police-officer | dancer | security-guard     | freelancer | social-worker | lawyer | mechanic |
| Pet     | snake   | frog    | guinea-pig | horse     | dog         | goldfish     | fish        |

