.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
House: colonial, modern, victorian, cottage, wooden, craftsman, futuristic
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, motorbike, roller, skateboard, snowmobile, trike
 1. the craftsman house is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
