 3. the futuristic house is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the modern house##1
 5. the craftsman house is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person driving the boat is the victorian house##1
 8. the wooden house is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the futuristic house##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the right of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| House   | colonial  | futuristic | cottage | wooden | craftsman     | modern | victorian |
| Transport     | snowmobile | roller      | trike | motorbike    | skateboard | jet-ski   | boat  |

