.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-8::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, dancing, filmmaking, gardening, puzzles, rock-climbing, woodworking
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: jazz, punk, dubstep, reggae, rock, country, ambient
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 2. the fan of ambient is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is the fan of dubstep##1
 4. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
 5. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the fan of reggae##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 8. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby       | dancing   | gardening | woodworking | rock-climbing | baking     | filmmaking | puzzles |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | country      | jazz        | ambient         | punk | reggae     | rock |

