The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, bike, boat, jet-ski, subway, tram, van
 1. the person driving the subway is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 4. the person driving the airplane is in the middle##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 6. the person driving the subway is the siglo-smoker##1
 7. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 9. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
11. the person driving the bike is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |   3    |    4     |   5    |     6      |   7    |
| Cigar        | tiparillo | bluemaster | baccarat | old-henry     | siglo | bongani | chaman |
