 4. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 5. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 7. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 8. the person watching musical movies is the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
10. the person playing domino is in the middle##1

