.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-15::.
City: rome, marseilles, new-york, boston, san-francisco, liverpool, prague
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, ice-hockey, rowing, rugby, snowboarding, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
 6. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
11. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |   2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6     |      7       |
| City    | marseilles | new-york | prague     | rome | boston | liverpool | san-francisco       |
| Sport   | baseball | rowing | ice-hockey | rugby     | water-polo  | climbing  | snowboarding |

